  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\nuser want to see unread messages after reopening the Status app, but when you close app and then open it with unread messages - they are marked as read after log in.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nuser can see amount of unread messages after reopening app\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nno unread messages after reopening app\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Start 1-1 chat\r\n- Leave some messages unread\r\n- Close app\r\n- Open app\r\n- Log in\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.11d441 (IOS), 0.9.10-441-gbd017457+ (Android), nightly 14/12/17\r\nCan be reproduced on release builds.\r\n\r\n* Operating System: reproducible for Android 7.0 and IOS 11.0.3\r\n\r\nVideo: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1gf67KpkKgqmp-doH-P3xNs39SCYF-DMg",
